Class Response

  • java.lang.Object
    • ph.com.globelabs.api.response.Response
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AccessTokenResponse, ChargeUserResponse, SendSmsResponse

    public class Response
extends java.lang.Object
    This class holds a response code and response message which represents the HTTP status code and reason phrase of the HttpResponse it was created from. This class also holds said HttpResponse.
